[[File:Police_protecting_the_statue_of_Lenin.jpg|thumbnail]]

2013年11月21日，由于乌克兰政府宣布延缓与[[欧洲联盟|欧洲联盟]]签署{{link-en|欧洲联盟联系国协定|European Union Association Agreement|联系国协定}}而转向接近俄罗斯<ref>{{cite news |url=http://world.people.com.cn/n/2013/1122/c1002-23619418.html |title=乌克兰暂停与欧盟签署联系国协定 普京表态愿意对话 |work=人民网 |date=2013-11-22 |accessdate=2014-03-21 |author=刘旭 |location=莫斯科 |language=zh-cn |deadurl=no |archive-date=2014-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140322001854/http://world.people.com.cn/n/2013/1122/c1002-23619418.html }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Ukraine drops EU plans and looks to Russia |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/europe/2013/11/ukraine-drops-eu-plans-looks-russia-20131121145417227621.html |publisher=Al Jazeera |language=en |date=2013-11-21 |accessdate=2014-03-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407062021/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/europe/2013/11/ukraine-drops-eu-plans-looks-russia-20131121145417227621.html |archivedate=2014-04-07 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，引发亲欧民众不满，乌克兰亲欧盟示威运动宣告开始。

最初的一个星期示威活动规模较小，唯11月24日（星期日）录得5万到20万人{{efn|此为媒体报道。12月6日乌克兰内务部对《基辅邮报》表示11月24日示威活动仅有2万2千人参加，而12月1日的示威活动仅有约8万人参加<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/euromaidan-rallies-in-ukrane-dec-6-coverage-333208.html |title=EuroMaidan rallies in Ukrane - Dec. 6 coverage |work=Kyiv Post |date=2013-12-07 |accessdate=2014-04-04 |language=en |quote=The Ministry’s department for public safety has counted 22,000 participants on Nov. 24 and more than 80,000 on Dec. 1. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140411203038/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/euromaidan-rallies-in-ukrane-dec-6-coverage-333208.html |archivedate=2014-04-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。}}参加的大型示威<ref>{{cite news|last=Sukhov |first=Oleg |title=Ukrainian Protests Compared to 2004 Orange Revolution |url=http://www.themoscowtimes.com/news/article/ukrainian-protests-compared-to-2004-orange-revolution/490205.html |work=Moscow Times |date=2013-11-25 |accessdate=2014-03-21 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140122123715/http://www.themoscowtimes.com/news/article/ukrainian-protests-compared-to-2004-orange-revolution/490205.html |archivedate=2014-01-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/13/11/25/n4018663.htm?photo=2 | title=数万乌克兰人抗议政府亲俄 拖延入欧协定 | work=大纪元 | date=2013-11-25 | accessdate=2014-03-21 | author=万平 | language=zh-cn | deadurl=no | archive-date=2014-03-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140322001700/http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/13/11/25/n4018663.htm?photo=2 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Mass rallies in Ukraine against government U-turn on EU |url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/2013/11/24/uk-ukraine-eu-idUKBRE9AN0C920131124 |date=2013-11-24 |work=Reuters |accessdate=2014-03-21 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140125153827/http://uk.reuters.com/article/2013/11/24/uk-ukraine-eu-idUKBRE9AN0C920131124 |archivedate=2014-01-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。不过，11月30日凌晨基辅警方和[[别尔库特部队|别尔库特部队]][[2013年基辅警民冲突|暴力驱逐]]了[[独立广场_(基辅)|独立广场]]的示威者，使得隔天在全市范围内爆发大规模流血冲突，12月1日录得约35万到50万的示威者。在总统办公厅前示威者甚至出动[[拖拉机|拖拉机]]冲击警方防线。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/euromaidan-rallies-on-dec-1-a-rowdy-afternoon-332780.html |title=EuroMaidan rallies on Dec. 1: A rowdy afternoon |work=Kyiv Post |date=2013-12-02 |accessdate=2014-03-30 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140411203503/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/euromaidan-rallies-on-dec-1-a-rowdy-afternoon-332780.html |archivedate=2014-04-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>两天的行动共造成包括警察和抗议者在内的190人受伤<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2013/12-02/5571133.shtml |title=乌克兰首都爆发警民冲突 受伤人数增至190人(图) |work=中国新闻网 |date=2013-12-02 |accessdate=2014-04-05 |language=zh-cn |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407095208/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2013/12-02/5571133.shtml |archivedate=2014-04-07 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

雕像倒塌前的上一个周日，12月1日晚上，示威者也试图拉倒这座雕像，但因为警方的防守而失败<ref name="IU20131208" />。尽管如此，还是有超过300名示威者用棍棒、石块和梯子攻击了守卫雕像的[[防暴警察|防暴警察]]，有至少2名警察因此受伤<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/kyiv/radical-protesters-clash-with-special-police-unit-at-lenin-monument-332772.html |title=Radical protesters clash with special police unit at Lenin monument (VIDEOS) |work=Kyiv Post |date=2013-12-01 |accessdate=2014-04-05 |author=Christopher J. Miller |location=Kiev |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140312025156/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/kyiv/radical-protesters-clash-with-special-police-unit-at-lenin-monument-332772.html |archivedate=2014-03-12 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

